/vo_full_103103-7-40"}],"nameLeft":"月夜","textLeft":"是的，她是筝曲社的社员@也是我的后辈"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":103801,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-7-41"}],"nameRight":"御影","textRight":"那！"},{"chara":[{"id":101801,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-7-42"}],"nameLeft":"月夜","textLeft":"是的"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800200,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-7-43"}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"突然互相使起眼色来了…@那个，我做了什么吗…？"},{"chara":[{"id":101801,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-7-44"}],"nameLeft":"月夜","textLeft":"不，反而应该说说@我有事想拜托你"},{"chara":[{"id":800200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-7-45"}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"是、是什么呢…"},{"chara":[{"id":101801,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-7-46"}],"nameLeft":"月夜","textLeft":"希望你能给我们的@「友好相处大作战」帮忙！"},{"autoTurnLast":2,"bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}